                        <item>
                <title>Re: A&amp;A Revised:  Germany [by SanFrancisco]</title>
                <link>http://www.tripleawarclub.org/modules/newbb/viewtopic.php?post_id=14500</link>
                <description>Strategy::A&amp;A Revised:  Germany&lt;br /&gt;
Bids: Empirically, the 80+% of the top 20 players bid 3 infantry. 1 in Ukr, 1 in Wrussia, 1 in Libya. Placing the infantry in belorussia instead of West Russia is an option. When placing in West Russia, Germany chooses to trade 1 additional infantry with Russia, so expected value of remaining Russia units in West Russia at R1 is 5 inf, 1 art, 1 tank, 1AA. Placing the infantry in WR is 0.13 better than placing in Belorussia under low luck settings.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The other bid option is 1 art, 1 tank.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;There are 3 contested areas between Germany and Russia R1:&lt;br /&gt;1. Russia attacks and destroys ukraine units&lt;br /&gt;2. Germany gets to stack Karelia safely&lt;br /&gt;3. Germany gets to stack Egypt&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;With usual probabilities, Germany gets one of these 3. The 3 infantry germany bid allows Russia to choose either 1 or 2. Africa bid gives Germany #3 with no choice by Russia.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;______&lt;br /&gt;Typical R1 buy is 10 inf, 2 tanks. 10 inf, 1 fig or 12 inf, 1 art are also viable but uncommon. The is no player in the top 20 that I&#039;m aware of who buys anything else R1. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;As a side note on why R1 Germany naval buys are bad. A classic example is a baltic carrier R1 is nearly an auto-win for allies given optimal play by both sides. The purchase sacrifices 5 infantry for Germany at an essential point. Allies are able to bully Germany, guaranteed stacking karelia R2, R3 and a very real risk of Ukr stack R5, baltic stack R6, and italy stack R7. UK buys 3 fighters a round and Germany is forced to choose to sharply escalate naval buys or lose the stack for almost free.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;----&lt;br /&gt;Why i&#039;m credible. I&#039;ve played over 600 games of Revised at the highest levels. Probably over 100 games exceeding 30 round, and experienced just about every outcome. transport sinking battleship, 40+ battleships, 1000 stack infs, etc. I&#039;ve written this content with a high level player in mind. Please message me or reply if you&#039;d like clarification.</description>
                <pubDate>Mon, 16 Nov 2015 21:03:18 -0600</pubDate>
                <guid>http://www.tripleawarclub.org/modules/newbb/viewtopic.php?post_id=14500</guid>
            </item>
